import React from "react"
import Box from '@mui/material/Box'
import { Typography } from "@mui/material"
import Paper from '@mui/material/Paper';
import Stack from '@mui/material/Stack';
import Chip from '@mui/material/Chip';
import { styled } from '@mui/material/styles';
import TextField from '@mui/material/TextField';

const Item = styled(Paper)(({ theme }) => ({
    backgroundColor: theme.palette.mode === 'dark' ? '#1A2027' : '#fff',
    ...theme.typography.body2,
    padding: theme.spacing(1),
    textAlign: 'center',
    color: theme.palette.text.secondary,
  }));

function Availability(props){
    return(
    <Box sx={{height:"100%", width:"100%" ,padding:'20px'}}>
        <Stack direction="row" spacing={2}>
            <Item> 
                
                <TextField disabled id="outlined-disabled" label="Location" defaultValue="Hello World">
                          odopgpodfopgpfopogf
                </TextField>
            </Item>
             <Item>
                 <TextField disabled id="outlined-disabled" label="Weather" defaultValue="Hello World">
                            odopgpodfopgpfopogf
                </TextField>
             </Item>
             <Item>
                     <Chip label="Available " variant="outlined"  />
             </Item>
             <Item>
                
             </Item>
            
        </Stack>
        <Chip label="Deletable" variant="outlined"  />
        <Chip label="Deletable" variant="outlined"  />
        <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5">
          
        </Typography>
        <Typography>
            
        </Typography>
    </Box>);
}
export default Availability;
